snippet.textDisplay:
Since some people don’t understand: if you don’t like a group or a song that’s totally fine, because we all have different tastes and you’re allowed to have your own opinion. However it’s not ok to drag them simply because you want to hate or belittle their achievements. They worked hard - all groups do - and deserve all the love and support from their fans.
Support who you want to support and that’s it. Let Nctzens love and rave about Nct since you‘d expect to be able to do so about your faves too.
I wish we‘d all just get along, all the hate is so unnecessary. Music is supposed to unite people not tear everyone apart!
snippet.textOriginal:
Since some people don’t understand: if you don’t like a group or a song that’s totally fine, because we all have different tastes and you’re allowed to have your own opinion. However it’s not ok to drag them simply because you want to hate or belittle their achievements. They worked hard - all groups do - and deserve all the love and support from their fans. 
Support who you want to support and that’s it. Let Nctzens love and rave about Nct since you‘d expect to be able to do so about your faves too. 
I wish we‘d all just get along, all the hate is so unnecessary. Music is supposed to unite people not tear everyone apart!
